#: ../../SO1.md:988
msgid ""
"Carbon stocks reflect the integration of multiple processes affecting "
"plant growth as well as decomposition, which together control the gains "
"and losses from terrestrial organic matter pools. They are elementary to "
"a wide range of ecosystem services, and their levels and dynamics are "
"reflective of soil type, land use and management practices."
