#: ../../SO1.md:1355
msgid ""
"**Change Assessment**: The change in extent of degradation between the "
"baseline and the reporting period is calculated as the difference between"
" the total area of degraded land in and the most recent reporting period,"
" and the baseline. It can be expressed as either the change in terms of "
"absolute area or as the change in terms of the proportion of degraded "
"area over the total land area (percentage)."
